Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.38,0:00:34.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:36.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.10,0:00:40.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么啊 是情书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.52,0:00:43.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是 这是普通的信而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:44.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大家现在不都这样玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:45.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.35,0:00:47.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:48.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:51.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,待会我也给由加莉写一封
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.32,0:00:52.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的好意我心领了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:55.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但上课的时候要认真听课啊 美奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:00:57.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比起学习 还是友情比较重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:01:01.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,最近女生之间流行写信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.49,0:01:02.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好像是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:05.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,说不定也有在写情书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.71,0:01:09.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她们写什么都很认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:10.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:12.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,情书吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.21,0:01:15.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,直接用嘴说就好了 居然还特意写在纸上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:17.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她们还真不嫌麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:19.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看来她们挺闲的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.35,0:01:28.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}对不起对不起对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.69,0:01:30.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 早苗 你干得太过了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.23,0:01:32.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一下就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:35.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还是要踢一脚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:38.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,开始上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:42.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,翻到课本76页
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:50.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学也在写信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:55.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,说到底高木同学也只是个普通的女生而已嘛
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——op——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:45.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你怎么了 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:56.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:58.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是信 谁送来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:00.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么要写给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:03.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,说不定也有在写情书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:06.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不不不 这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:07.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定是谁的恶作剧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:13.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这说不定是高木同学的恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:15.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 肯定是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:18.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:21.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 要是弄错了该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要不是高木同学写的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:25.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一旦我收到信件的事情暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:27.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定又会被高木同学捉弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天天气不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:42.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是不是在瞒着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:49.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但感觉你好可疑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,脸还那么红
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:53.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是你的错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:55.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是错觉就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你为什么不翻开课本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:00.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个嘛…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:03.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这和你脸红有关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:05.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没有 我的脸也没有红
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:08.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:10.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都说了什么事也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:15.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是我的错觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:20.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还有 夹在书里的那封信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:22.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是我放的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:27.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,果然是她干的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:33.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这种把戏 我完全看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:35.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:39.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我只是装不知道而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:42.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不看看里面写了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:44.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么 里面写了东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:46.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:51.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,反正又是捉弄我的内容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:56.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你干嘛不说话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:06:00.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那既然你写了 我就看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:02.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你现在看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:05.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:08.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为这节课下课之后就放学了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:10.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,想你在那之前答复我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,答 答复？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:19.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,需要作出回复的信件 也就是说里面有提问
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:22.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,内容难道不只是恶作剧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,说不定也有在写情书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:28.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也就是说有可能是情书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:30.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:37.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道是情书什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:41.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又默不出声吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:45.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我看 我会看的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:48.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看了就行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:53.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,照那么说 里面写的肯定是恶作剧之类的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:56.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那无论里面写了什么 我都要保持镇定不被她捉弄到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:58.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,堂堂正正地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:01.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:02.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:06.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,虽然肯定是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:09.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但要真是情书的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:13.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我该…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:23.13,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs100\fad(200,0)\frx8\fry0\frz352.3\move(641.6,408,643.2,308.8,195,4908)}给西片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:23.13,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs100\frz345.8\frx2\fry4\move(657.6,917.2,660.8,840.4,195,4908)\fad(200,0)}今天一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,直接跟我说不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:38.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,现在流行写信嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:45.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且 我也想看看你会有怎样的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:49.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你果然是在捉弄我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:50.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:53.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,吵死了 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:09.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,入学典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:20.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀 麻烦你专门跑一趟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没什么 我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:24.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:28.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,新生 你的名字叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:30.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,您问我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:32.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我叫西片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:36.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 祝贺你入学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:41.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:45.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在接下来的一年里 你们就是一起学习的伙伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:48.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我不会要求你们每时每刻都保持融洽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:52.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但希望你们尽可能和谐相处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:55.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是掉到哪里去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:59.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嘛 刚开学也没有什么需要唠叨的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:03.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,突然就来了个睡过头的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:05.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:08.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的胆量我倒是挺佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:09.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:10.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:13.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我叫西片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:16.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算了 坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:18.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:26.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好显眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:28.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在被定性为迟到型角色之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:31.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,得赶紧和大家打好交道 解开误会才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:37.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,田边老师 能打扰一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:41.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,车子好像晚点才到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:44.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,迟到了吗 那仪式也要推迟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:46.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:50.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,现在入学典礼的准备时间延长了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:52.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好像会耽搁不少时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:54.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在这期间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:58.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我们来决定座位顺序
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:07.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:10.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,偏偏抽到了最后一排最角落的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:12.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,放在平时会是件令人高兴的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:14.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但对现在的我来说只有坏处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:16.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,本来就一个人也不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:20.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,现在左边和后面都没有人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:22.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且旁边坐的还是女生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你真的睡过头了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:29.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她向我搭话了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为老师好像跟你说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:36.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,该怎么说好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是没有迟到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:41.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我都明明准时到学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:45.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都怪一个叫高木同学的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 所有人去体育馆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:52.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,安静一点 不要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:54.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:59.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:02.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:08.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:15.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你们总有一天会得到选举权这笔无价的财富
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:20.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,最重要的是要选择值得信赖的政治家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:25.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,请务必 让爸爸和妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:30.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,演讲太长了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:30.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:33.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大叔的演讲就是长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:36.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,无论在小学还是中学都没什么变化嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:40.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不过开学第一天就迟到 你也是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:42.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要吵了 回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:52.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:58.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:00.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,快点坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:05.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天就到此结束了 明天开始正式上课
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:08.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要因为是开学典礼就得意忘形 要乖乖回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:11.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:17.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我来猜猜今天西片迟到的理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:20.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是一次就猜中 那就算我赢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:26.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一次是猜不中的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:31.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是去送还失物了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:33.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,诶 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:35.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 你太吵了西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:37.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:41.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么你会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:49.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:56.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:59.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,做自我介绍的时候你不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:09.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的反应是怎么回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:12.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说 那一块很吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:13.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:24.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你帮我捡回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:28.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,以后请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:34.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:37.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,换座位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:42.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,七十二 七十三
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:49.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,七十四 七十五
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:57.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有点肌肉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:11.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:41.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她还没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:45.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:48.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:53.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:57.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天要换座位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:05.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:06.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,班会课的时候换
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:09.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,班会课不是第一节吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:24.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}高木同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:24.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:30.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:31.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:38.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为 好久没有换过座位了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:49.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,虽然也有值得期待的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:54.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但我还是觉得西片旁边的位置比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:00.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她又要捉弄我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:03.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:20.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所有人都抽签了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:24.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 按签上面写的调换座位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:26.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片是多少号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:28.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,29号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:32.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊 又是在最后一排呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:33.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:37.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我在中间那列的第一位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:39.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:43.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我们离得好远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:46.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:49.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉 考试的时候告诉我答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:54.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不对 一般来说那算抄袭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是相互帮助啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:57.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈要怎么帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:16:59.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我从后面给你加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:02.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哟 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:04.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你坐这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:05.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 是对面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:09.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊 要是在附近就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:10.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:17.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我最近视力变差了 不知道能不能看清黑板呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:37.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,旁边坐的原来是西片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:39.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:42.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:46.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了 你这反应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.13,0:17:50.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没什么 不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:56.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只是不能和中井坐到一块 有点失落而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:02.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,中井的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:05.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:09.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有谁能和我换换座位吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:13.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,坐着讲台的正前方 我要怎么偷吃午饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:16.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没有正当理由的话 不可以换座位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:19.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还有木村 你跟我来教员室一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:21.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:24.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,讲台正前方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:29.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我觉得还是西片旁边的位置比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:48.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,木村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:50.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我视力不太好 我们交换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:53.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不行 我已经换好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:04.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:09.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:11.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:21.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:24.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我把座位换到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:25.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,诶 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:31.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我让中井同学和木村同学以看不见黑板为由换了座位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为中井坐到了最前面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:37.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原本坐他旁边的我就和真野换了位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:40.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为真野个子小 坐前面比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:43.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:48.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 你原本打算换到我旁边的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:55.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那个 因为我看不清黑板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:58.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:05.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:07.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,开始上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:08.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,把课本拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:10.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:12.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片想跟我说什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:16.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,从早上开始 你就一直想和我说些什么似的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:27.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个 抱歉还晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:29.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:31.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是暑假那时的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:32.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:34.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:36.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,入学典礼那天的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:37.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你还记得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:40.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片才是 亏你还记得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:43.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:46.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:49.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我把它洗干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:55.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:57.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不过 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:01.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我是指各种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:04.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比如把手帕还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:06.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又能一起坐什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:09.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那个…各种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:12.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,以后也请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:13.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I do not say
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:14.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:17.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}在这篇文章里 do是一般现在时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:21.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}这时把它变成过去式的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:47.70,Takagisan-huamian-1,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fs180\pos(1098,310)}给高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:47.70,Takagisan-huamian-1,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fs180\pos(720,494)}非常感谢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:17.40,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:21.82,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:32.17,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:40.97,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}校庭で君のことを一番に見つけて今日は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:49.27,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて話しかけようか？ ちょっと考えるの楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:52.23,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風に揺らされるカーテン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:57.61,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不意打ちに当たる日差し
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:03:01.49,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}眩しそうな顔を笑ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:05.41,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}照れて伏せちゃうのね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:13.50,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}憂鬱なテストも吹き飛ばせるような
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:21.80,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ねえ、二人で秘密の約束をしたいなって提案です
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:27.22,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:31.19,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:41.45,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:17.40,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}会错意了也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:21.82,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 这样想着却不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:32.17,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}弥漫在周围的那阵幽香 想在你的身边静静感受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:40.97,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}在校园的庭院 第一个发现你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:49.27,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}今天要和你说些什么呢 即便是想着这些也是一种乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:52.23,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}窗帘随风起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:57.61,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不经意地投入一束阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:03:01.49,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那美丽的容颜笑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:05.41,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}羞得我抬不起头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:13.50,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}风儿喧嚣 似要吹散考试的忧郁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:21.80,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}呐 我想要和你一起 立下两人的秘密约定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:27.22,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}会错意了也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:31.19,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 这样想着却不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:41.45,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}弥漫在周围的那阵幽香 想在你的身边静静感受
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:53.41,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}My love is forever
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:59.59,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}あなたと出逢った頃のように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.59,0:22:03.34,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}季節が変わっても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:10.51,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}きっと色褪せないはずだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.49,0:22:34.00,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}ダイアリー会える日しるしつけてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.45,0:22:38.79,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}なんだか不思議ね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:49.14,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}今まで以上に夢中になれるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:56.48,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}夏の恋の魔法のせいかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.94,0:22:59.44,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}My love is forever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:05.61,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}あなたと出逢った頃のように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.61,0:23:09.20,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}いつまでもいたいね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.24,0:23:13.08,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}ときめき大事にして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.08,0:23:17.79,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}青く澄んだ瞳に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.96,0:23:21.63,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}この胸は高鳴るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:25.46,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}季節が変わっても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.46,0:23:32.76,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}きっと色褪せないはずだよ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:53.41,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}My love is forever
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:59.59,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}宛如你我相逢之时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.59,0:22:03.34,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}就算四季交替
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:10.51,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}也绝不会褪色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.49,0:22:34.00,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}在日记里标上和你相会的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.45,0:22:38.79,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}总有些不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:49.14,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}沉迷其中 更甚过往
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:56.48,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}是因为夏天的恋爱魔法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.94,0:22:59.44,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}My love is forever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:05.61,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}宛如你我相逢之时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.61,0:23:09.20,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}想和你厮守一生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.24,0:23:13.08,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}珍惜一点一滴的感动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.08,0:23:17.79,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}湛蓝清澄的眼瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.96,0:23:21.63,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}心中澎湃不已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:25.46,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}就算四季交替
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.46,0:23:32.76,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}也绝不会褪色
